caption.p: Effects of rFIP-mco on A549 and HepG2 cell proliferation. A549 (A) or HepG2 (B) cells treated with gradient concentrations of rFIP-mco. Cell proliferation was determined by a Cell-Counting Kit-8 assay for 0, 24, 48, 72 and 96Â h. * P < 0.05 vs. control groups (untreated cells). IC 50 value of rFIP-mco for A549 (C) and HepG2 (D) cells were also determined.
